             sworn.</p>
               <p>The 8th day of this month, it was Wednesday was se'nnight, the dust came in upon the beasts; I looked up, and saw the lead was taken off; then I got up, and missed it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920215-14-person243">
                  HUGH
                   O'DONNEL
